original_title: The Original Latin Kings of Comedy
overview: This stand up special features material from five of the most famous Hispanic standup comics of their era. Paul_Rodriguez (A.K.A. Pablo), George_Lopez (The_George_Lopez_Show), Cheech_Marin (of Cheech and Chong fame), Alex_Reymundo, and Joey_Medina deliver material on a variety of topics that will seem familiar to audiences of every race.
title: The Original Latin Kings of Comedy
